quran[6{c,v,t}:
5,77,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! apne deen mein na-haq ghallo nah karo aur aُ noon logon ke takhayulaat ki pairwi nah karo jo tum se pehlay khud gumraah hue aur bahuton ko gumraah kya, aur"" sawa as sabeelse bhatak gay"
5,78,bani Israel mein se jin logon ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki unn par DAWOD aur eesa Ibn maryam ki zabaan se laanat ki gayi kyunkay woh sarkash hogaye thay aur zyadtyan karne lagey thay
5,79,"onhon ne aik dosray ko buray af-aal ke irtikaab se rokna chore diya tha, bura tarz amal tha jo onhon ne ikhtiyar kya"
5,80,"aaj tum unn mein bakasrat aisay log dekhte ho jo ( ahal imaan ke muqaabla mein ) kufar ki himayat o rafaqat karte hain yaqeenan bohat bura injaam hai jis ki tayari unn ke nafso-n ne unn ke liye ki hai, Allah unn par ghazab naak ho gaya hai aur woh daimi azaab mein mubtala honay walay hain"
5,81,agar fi al waqea yeh log Allah aurPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamaur uss cheez ke maan-ne walay hotay jo paighambar par nazil hui thi to kabhi ( ahal imaan ke muqablay mein ) kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq nah banatay magar un mein se to beshtar log khuda ki itaat se nikal chuke hain
5,82,"tum ahal imaan ki adawat mein sab se ziyada sakht yahood aur mushriqeen ko pao ge, aur imaan laane walon ke liye dosti mein qareeb tar unn logon ko pa o ge jinhon ne kaha tha ke hum nasari hain yeh iss wajah se ke un mein ibadat guzaar aalam aur tarik al-dunia faqeer paye jatay hain aur unn mein ghuroor nafs nahi hai"
